  "combined_text": "--- Main Page ---\nEdgar's P&P\n0\nAn unconventional speakeasy in the heart of Midtown Atlanta\nTucked below The Georgian Terrace in midtown\nAtlanta, you’ll be welcomed by an intimate, prohibition-style whiskey bar unlike any other loved by locals and visitors alike. Featuring barrel-aged cocktails, local craft beers and boldly imagined bar bites, we’ve got something catering to every mood and palate. Come on in, pull up a seat and Edgar’s will do the rest.\nMENUS\nAll Day\nDrinks\nUpcoming events\nSuper Bowl Specials\nFebruary 8th | Watch Party\nBeer Buckets | $25\nDraft Beer | 10% OFF\nPizza & Wings | 10% OFF\nNational Tequila Day\nFebruary 22nd  | All Day\nCelebrate lime, tequila, and salt with $7 Margarita Special!\nGallery\nPrivate Events\nLooking for the perfect venue for your next unforgettable event? Our private spaces are available for buyouts and designed to offer an exclusive and intimate setting, tailored to meet your needs. Whether it's a corporate gathering, a milestone celebration, or a romantic occasion, our venues provide the ideal backdrop, complete with exceptional service and attention to detail. Make your event truly memorable with our sophisticated and versatile spaces.\nContact Us\nJoin Us Upstairs\nIndulge in a culinary experience in Atlanta, Georgia, at our sister restaurant, where you can discover a world of delectable flavors paired with meticulously handcrafted cocktails that will captivate your taste buds and leave you longing for more.\nLearn More\nVisit Us\n659 Peachtree Street NE\nAtlanta, Georgia 30308\nHours\nMonday – Thursday 5 pm – 11 pm\nFriday – Sunday 2 pm – 11 pm\nPhone\n(404) 897-1991\nOther Locations\nEdgar's Proof & Provision\n15 E. Liberty St.\nSavannah, Georgia 31401\n(912) 443-2000\nPart & Parcel\n1700 Smith St.\nHouston, TX 77002\n(713) 739-8800\n\n--- Page: /s/Edgars-P_P-Menu-1-part-1.pdf ---\n%PDF-1.6\r%����\n1 0 obj\n<\n>\nendobj\n2 0 obj\n<\n>stream\n2024-08-20T19:32:09Z\n2024-08-20T19:32:09Z\n2